(38, 'My Girlfriend is an Alien', 'The alien girl Chai Xiaoqi from \"Cape Town Planet\" meets the CEO Fang Leng, who suffers from \"heterosexual amnesia on rainy days\", accidentally loses her beacon, and is trapped on Earth.\r\n\r\nChai Xiaoqi is not only an alien but also an amazing girl who will fall into a \"boy crazy state\" once she inhales the hormones emitted by men on Earth.\r\n\r\nShe experiences all kinds of funny and hilarious encounters, which will perfectly restore the nymphomaniac girls psychology of flirting with men for the audience.\r\n\r\nIn order to survive on the earth, Chai Xiaoqi will also use her various superpowers to solve unexpected trouble one after another.\r\n\r\nFang Leng is a different kind of boss. Once it rains, he will forget the girls who appeared on his side. So he has a variety of hilarious \"battles of wits\" with the Chai Xiaoqi.', '', 'mgia.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/4QcHHal-pt4?si=suh63c4ZDwn5mJbq', '', 'shizu', '2024-01-17', 1, 22, '#alien,#love,#romanceofspace', '00:21:52'),
(39, 'Put Your Head on My Shoulder', '\"Put Your Head on My Shoulder\" is a Chinese romantic drama that revolves around the lives of two individuals, Si Tu Mo and Gu Wei Yi, as they navigate the complexities of love, friendship, and personal growth. Set against the backdrop of a university campus, the series unfolds the endearing journey of these two characters who find themselves entangled in a web of emotions.\r\n\r\nSi Tu Mo, a cheerful and ambitious young woman, is focused on her studies and career aspirations. However, her life takes an unexpected turn when she finds herself living under the same roof as Gu Wei Yi, an intelligent but emotionally reserved engineering student. As the two opposites attract, their undeniable chemistry sparks a series of humorous and heartwarming moments.\r\n\r\nThe drama explores the nuances of relationships, highlighting the challenges and joys of falling in love for the first time. With a mix of lighthearted humor and touching moments, \"Put Your Head on My Shoulder\" invites viewers to join the characters on their journey of self-discovery, love, and the pursuit of happiness. As Si Tu Mo and Gu Wei Yi navigate the ups and downs of romance, the series beautifully captures the essence of youthful exuberance and the transformative power of love.', '', 'pyhoms.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/FJNqLXmtGKU?si=t04qlrvqL27GfsjP', '', 'shizu', '2024-01-17', 1, 22, '#love,#romance,#science', '00:42:53'),
