(73, 'Telescopes 100 Years Ago', 'In the early 20th century, astronomers embarked on a journey of discovery, armed with telescopes that, by today\'s standards, may seem rudimentary but were instrumental in unraveling the mysteries of the cosmos. Let\'s step back in time and explore the telescopes of a century ago, their technology, capabilities, and the groundbreaking discoveries they facilitated.', 'Exploring the Universe: Telescopes a Century Ago\n\nIn the early 20th century, astronomers embarked on a journey of discovery, armed with telescopes that, by today\'s standards, may seem rudimentary but were instrumental in unraveling the mysteries of the cosmos. Let\'s step back in time and explore the telescopes of a century ago, their technology, capabilities, and the groundbreaking discoveries they facilitated.\n\nThe Era of Refracting Telescopes\n\nAt the turn of the 20th century, refracting telescopes dominated the astronomical landscape. These telescopes utilized lenses to gather and focus light, offering astronomers a glimpse into the distant reaches of space. Among the most renowned examples was the 60-inch Hale Telescope at Mount Wilson Observatory, which, upon its completion in 1908, held the title of the world\'s largest telescope.\n\nAdvancements in Reflecting Telescopes\n\nReflecting telescopes, which employ mirrors to collect and focus light, also made significant strides during this period. Innovations such as the Cassegrain and Newtonian designs improved optical performance and enabled astronomers to observe fainter and more distant celestial objects. The 100-inch Hooker Telescope, also located at Mount Wilson Observatory, exemplified the capabilities of reflecting telescopes, offering unparalleled views of the cosmos.\n\nObservational Discoveries\n\nArmed with these telescopes, astronomers embarked on ambitious observational campaigns, revolutionizing our understanding of the universe. Edwin Hubble\'s groundbreaking observations with the Hooker Telescope provided compelling evidence for the expanding universe and the existence of galaxies beyond our own Milky Way. Meanwhile, astronomers such as Annie Jump Cannon and Cecilia Payne-Gaposchkin used refracting telescopes to classify stars and unravel the mysteries of stellar evolution.\n\nChallenges and Limitations\n\nDespite their advancements, telescopes of a century ago faced significant challenges and limitations. Atmospheric turbulence, light pollution, and technological constraints hindered astronomers\' ability to observe faint objects and achieve high-resolution imaging. Nevertheless, astronomers persevered, pushing the boundaries of observational astronomy and laying the groundwork for future generations of telescopes and scientific discoveries.\n\nLegacy and Inspiration\n\nThe telescopes of a century ago left an indelible legacy, inspiring generations of astronomers and shaping our understanding of the cosmos. Their pioneering work laid the foundation for the construction of larger, more sophisticated telescopes, such as the Hubble Space Telescope and the forthcoming James Webb Space Telescope, which continue to push the boundaries of astronomical research.\n\nConclusion\n\nIn retrospect, the telescopes of 100 years ago may pale in comparison to their modern counterparts in terms of size and sophistication. However, their impact on the field of astronomy and our collective understanding of the universe is immeasurable. As we reflect on their legacy, we are reminded of the enduring spirit of exploration and discovery that drives humanity\'s quest to unravel the mysteries of the cosmos.\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'blog_sci_telescope.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/cjFRYkYG1HU?si=KpRw7OM4-1fbSGSc\" title=\"YouTube video player', '', 'jenish', '2014-04-15', 2, 15, 'telescope', '00:05:00'),
(74, 'Fiber Optics Bring You Internet.', 'Fiber Optics Bring You Internet. Now Theyre Also Listening to Trains\r\nDistributed acoustic sensing looks for disturbances in fiber to detect earthquakes and even insects. Can it also improve rail safety?', 'Unveiling the Wonders of Fiber Optics: Powering the Internet Age\n\nIn an increasingly interconnected world, the backbone of our digital infrastructure lies in the marvels of fiber optics. From enabling lightning-fast internet speeds to revolutionizing telecommunications, fiber optics has emerged as a cornerstone of the modern era. Join us as we delve into the fascinating world of fiber optics and explore how it brings the internet to your fingertips.\n\nUnraveling the Science of Fiber Optics\n\nAt its core, fiber optics harnesses the principles of light propagation through transparent fibers made of glass or plastic. These fibers, thinner than a human hair, are designed to carry light signals over long distances with minimal loss or distortion. By transmitting data in the form of light pulses, fiber optics achieves speeds and bandwidths far exceeding those of traditional copper-based cables.\n\nThe Birth of High-Speed Internet\n\nThe widespread adoption of fiber optics has transformed the landscape of internet connectivity, paving the way for high-speed broadband services that power our digital lives. Fiber-optic networks, capable of transmitting data at speeds measured in gigabits per second, enable seamless streaming of high-definition video, ultra-responsive online gaming, and instantaneous access to vast repositories of information.\n\nEmpowering Telecommunications\n\nBeyond internet connectivity, fiber optics plays a pivotal role in revolutionizing telecommunications infrastructure. Optical fiber cables form the backbone of global communication networks, facilitating the transmission of voice, data, and multimedia content across vast distances. From international submarine cables to metropolitan fiber rings, fiber optics underpins the seamless exchange of information that drives our interconnected world.\n\nApplications Beyond Connectivity\n\nThe impact of fiber optics extends far beyond internet connectivity and telecommunications. In fields such as medicine, fiber-optic sensors enable minimally invasive diagnostic procedures and precise monitoring of vital signs. In manufacturing, fiber-optic inspection systems ensure the quality and integrity of industrial processes. From aerospace to automotive industries, fiber optics finds applications in diverse fields, driving innovation and efficiency.\n\nChallenges and Future Prospects\n\nWhile fiber optics holds immense promise, it also presents challenges, including the cost of infrastructure deployment and the need for ongoing maintenance and upgrades. Nevertheless, ongoing advancements in fiber-optic technology, such as the development of hollow-core fibers and photonic integrated circuits, promise to further enhance performance and expand the reach of fiber-optic networks.\n\nConclusion\n\nAs we navigate the digital age, fiber optics stands as a testament to human ingenuity and innovation. From powering high-speed internet connections to revolutionizing global telecommunications, fiber optics has become indispensable to our modern way of life. As we look to the future, the continued advancement of fiber-optic technology holds the promise of even greater connectivity, efficiency, and opportunity for generations to come.', 'blog_sci_fiber.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/cR1FyHv_rJE?si=KtkOGaoBDPW-t8Na\" title=\"YouTube video player', '', 'jenish', '2024-01-31', 2, 15, 'fiber', '00:05:00'),
(75, 'Second Brain', 'Unpicking the Mystery of the Bodys Second Brain\r\nSitting alongside the neurons in your enteric nervous system are underappreciated glial cells, which play key roles in digestion and disease that scientists are only just starting to understand.', 'Unveiling the Concept of the Second Brain: Your Gut\n\nIn recent years, scientific research has shed light on an extraordinary aspect of human physiology: the \"second brain\" residing in our gut. Far from being a mere digestive organ, the gut harbors a complex network of neurons and neurotransmitters that exert a profound influence on our physical and mental well-being. Join us as we explore the fascinating world of the second brain and its implications for health and happiness.\n\nThe Gut-Brain Axis: A Bidirectional Communication Highway\n\nThe communication between the gut and the brain is facilitated by the gut-brain axis, a complex network of nerves, hormones, and biochemical signaling pathways. This bidirectional communication highway allows the gut to send signals to the brain and vice versa, influencing everything from mood and emotions to immune function and inflammation.\n\nThe Role of the Microbiome: Guardians of Gut Health\n\nCentral to the functioning of the second brain is the gut microbiome, a diverse ecosystem of trillions of microorganisms that inhabit our digestive tract. These \"friendly\" bacteria play a crucial role in maintaining gut health, aiding in digestion, synthesizing essential nutrients, and modulating the immune system. Emerging research suggests that disturbances in the gut microbiome may contribute to a wide range of health conditions, including depression, anxiety, and autoimmune diseases.\n\nThe Gut-Brain Connection: Implications for Mental Health\n\nThe influence of the gut on mental health has garnered increasing attention in the field of psychiatry and neuroscience. Studies have revealed intimate connections between gut health and conditions such as depression, anxiety, and even neurodegenerative diseases like Alzheimer\'s. The gut microbiome produces neurotransmitters such as serotonin and gamma-aminobutyric acid (GABA), which play crucial roles in regulating mood and emotional states.\n\nNurturing Your Second Brain: Strategies for Gut Health\n\nMaintaining a healthy second brain requires attention to both diet and lifestyle factors. Consuming a diverse array of fiber-rich foods, fermented foods, and prebiotics nourishes the gut microbiome and promotes a balanced microbial ecosystem. Additionally, managing stress, getting adequate sleep, and staying physically active contribute to overall gut health and well-being.\n\nHarnessing the Power of the Second Brain\n\nAs our understanding of the gut-brain connection deepens, so too does the potential for innovative therapies and interventions. Probiotics, prebiotics, and other gut-targeted interventions hold promise for managing mental health conditions and improving overall well-being. By nurturing our second brain, we can unlock new avenues for promoting health, happiness, and vitality.\n\nConclusion\n\nThe concept of the second brain underscores the profound interconnectedness of mind and body. By recognizing the pivotal role of the gut in shaping our physical and mental health, we gain valuable insights into strategies for fostering wellness and resilience. As we continue to unravel the mysteries of the gut-brain axis, we pave the way for a future where holistic approaches to health and healing flourish.\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'blog_sci_braicell.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/1karSBbkTXw?si=ZJ7xMqfjh8rz1nyW\" title=\"YouTube video player', '', 'prakash', '2024-01-14', 2, 15, 'braincell', '00:05:00'),
(76, 'Love and Lemons', 'Hello, we\'re Jeanine and Jack.\r\nWe love to eat, travel, cook, and eat some more! We create & photograph vegetarian recipes from our home in Chicago, while our shiba pups eat the kale stems that fall on the kitchen floor.', 'Embracing Love and Lemons: A Culinary Journey of Flavor and Freshness\n\nIn the realm of culinary delights, there exists a magical pairing that transcends seasons and palates  love and lemons. From zesty appetizers to tangy desserts, the humble lemon infuses dishes with a burst of brightness and vitality, while love adds an extra layer of warmth and affection to every creation. Join us as we explore the harmonious marriage of love and lemons and discover the culinary wonders that await.\n\nThe Power of Citrus\n\nAt the heart of the love and lemons saga lies the versatile citrus fruit  the lemon. With its vibrant yellow hue and tangy flavor profile, the lemon has long been cherished by chefs and home cooks alike for its ability to elevate dishes to new heights. Whether squeezed over grilled fish, zested into pasta, or incorporated into decadent desserts, lemons add a refreshing and invigorating element that tantalizes the taste buds and invigorates the senses.\n\nRecipes From the Heart\n\nIn the kitchen, love and lemons work in perfect harmony to create dishes that not only nourish the body but also feed the soul. From a simple yet satisfying lemon garlic roasted chicken to a vibrant and refreshing lemon basil pasta salad, each recipe is crafted with care and intention, infusing every bite with a sense of joy and connection. And let\'s not forget about dessert  who can resist the irresistible allure of a tangy lemon tart or a fluffy lemon poppyseed cake?\n\nA Feast for the Senses\n\nAs you embark on your culinary journey with love and lemons, take a moment to savor the experience with all your senses. Inhale the fragrant aroma of freshly squeezed lemon juice, revel in the vibrant colors of citrus-infused dishes, and delight in the symphony of flavors that dance across your palate with each bite. Whether cooking for yourself or sharing a meal with loved ones, let the magic of love and lemons transform every moment into a celebration of life and nourishment.\n\nThe Gift of Giving\n\nIn addition to delighting the senses, love and lemons also hold the power to uplift and inspire others. Consider sharing your favorite lemon-infused recipes with friends and family, or surprise a loved one with a homemade lemon treat as a gesture of affection. In a world filled with hustle and bustle, a simple act of kindness infused with the essence of love and lemons can brighten someone\'s day and remind them of the beauty that surrounds us.\n\nConclusion\n\nAs we bid adieu to our culinary adventure with love and lemons, let us carry forward the lessons learned in the kitchen  that the simplest ingredients have the power to transform ordinary moments into extraordinary experiences, and that love, like a freshly squeezed lemon, adds a touch of brightness and zest to everything it touches. So go forth, dear readers, and embrace the magic of love and lemons in your own culinary creations, and may your kitchen always be filled with laughter, flavor, and joy. Cheers to love, lemons, and the endless possibilities that lie ahead!', 'blog_food_lemon.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/JP3QjhrUPd0?si=HL8zpHqVW-Cky_U7\" title=\"YouTube video player', '', 'piksu', '2020-04-29', 2, 14, 'food', '00:05:00'),
(77, 'Mor Mu Dong Restaurant', 'Food You Must Eat in Phuket, Thailand!', 'Savoring the Flavors of Tradition: Exploring Mor Mu Dong Restaurant\n\nNestled in the heart of [location], Mor Mu Dong Restaurant beckons food enthusiasts on a culinary journey through the rich tapestry of Thai cuisine. With its unassuming facade and warm ambiance, this culinary gem offers more than just a meal; it provides a window into the soul of Thai gastronomy. Join us as we embark on a virtual tour of Mor Mu Dong and discover the tantalizing flavors that await within.\n\nA Culinary Oasis\n\nAs you step through the doors of Mor Mu Dong, you are greeted by the enticing aromas of freshly prepared Thai dishes wafting from the kitchen. The restaurant\'s inviting atmosphere, adorned with traditional Thai decor and soothing music, sets the stage for a memorable dining experience. Whether you\'re seeking a casual lunch with friends or a romantic dinner for two, Mor Mu Dong caters to every occasion with its welcoming ambiance and attentive service.\n\nThe Artistry of Thai Cuisine\n\nAt Mor Mu Dong, the menu is a celebration of Thailand\'s culinary heritage, showcasing a diverse array of dishes bursting with flavor and authenticity. From fragrant curries and zesty salads to succulent grilled meats and aromatic stir-fries, each dish is crafted with care and precision, using the finest ingredients sourced from local markets and trusted suppliers. Whether you\'re a fan of classic Thai favorites or eager to explore new culinary horizons, Mor Mu Dong offers something to tantalize every palate.\n\nSignature Dishes\n\nAmong the highlights of Mor Mu Dong\'s menu are its signature dishes, beloved by locals and visitors alike. Indulge in the rich and creamy goodness of Green Curry Chicken, or savor the complex flavors of Pad Thai, expertly prepared with a perfect balance of sweet, sour, and savory notes. For seafood lovers, the Tom Yum Goong soup offers a tantalizing blend of spicy and sour flavors, while the Grilled Pork Neck provides a satisfyingly smoky and tender culinary experience.\n\nA Feast for the Senses\n\nDining at Mor Mu Dong is more than just a meal; it\'s a feast for the senses. From the vibrant colors of freshly prepared ingredients to the tantalizing aromas that dance through the air, every aspect of the dining experience is designed to delight and inspire. Pair your meal with a refreshing Thai iced tea or a crisp Singha beer, and let the flavors of Thailand transport you to a culinary paradise.\n\nConclusion\n\nMor Mu Dong Restaurant embodies the essence of Thai hospitality and culinary excellence, offering a memorable dining experience that celebrates the rich flavors and traditions of Thailand. Whether you\'re a seasoned food enthusiast or a curious traveler eager to explore the wonders of Thai cuisine, Mor Mu Dong invites you to embark on a gastronomic adventure you won\'t soon forget.\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'blog_food_thai.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/iv0Uq2iIuCY?si=8WLARP8LhhrktLGd\" title=\"YouTube video player', '', 'piksu', '2023-11-14', 2, 14, 'thaifood', '00:05:00'),
(78, 'Aloo Phulkopir Dalna', 'Aloo Phulkopir Dalna  Bengali Cauliflower Potato Curry', 'Exploring Aloo Phulkopir Dalna: A Taste of Bengali Comfort Food\n\nIn the rich tapestry of Bengali cuisine, Aloo Phulkopir Dalna stands as a beloved classic  a comforting and flavorful dish that embodies the essence of home-cooked goodness. Rooted in tradition yet versatile in its execution, this hearty curry brings together the humble potato (aloo) and cauliflower (phulkopi) in a tantalizing medley of spices and aromatics. Join us as we delve into the world of Aloo Phulkopir Dalna and uncover the secrets behind its irresistible allure.\n\nA Culinary Tradition\n\nAloo Phulkopir Dalna holds a special place in Bengali households, where it is often prepared with love and care to nourish both body and soul. The dish is characterized by its delicate balance of flavors, with the sweetness of the cauliflower complementing the earthiness of the potatoes, all brought together in a rich and aromatic gravy. Served alongside steaming hot rice or fluffy rotis, Aloo Phulkopir Dalna is a comforting meal that speaks to the heart.\n\nThe Art of Preparation\n\nThe magic of Aloo Phulkopir Dalna lies in its simplicity, yet the dish is not without its intricacies. To achieve the perfect balance of flavors and textures, the potatoes and cauliflower are first sauted with onions, ginger, and garlic, allowing them to absorb the fragrant spices. A blend of turmeric, cumin, coriander, and garam masala lends depth and complexity to the dish, while a touch of green chili adds a hint of heat. Finished with a splash of water and a sprinkle of fresh cilantro, Aloo Phulkopir Dalna is ready to grace the table with its irresistible aroma and mouthwatering flavor.\n\nA Celebration of Seasonal Ingredients\n\nOne of the hallmarks of Bengali cuisine is its reliance on fresh, seasonal ingredients, and Aloo Phulkopir Dalna is no exception. Traditionally prepared during the winter months when cauliflower is in abundance, this comforting curry showcases the best of what the season has to offer. The crisp texture of the cauliflower and the creamy flesh of the potatoes are a testament to the bountiful harvest, while the warm spices evoke the cozy comforts of home on chilly evenings.\n\nA Feast for the Senses\n\nAs you savor each spoonful of Aloo Phulkopir Dalna, allow yourself to be transported to the bustling streets of Kolkata, where the tantalizing aroma of spices fills the air and the sound of sizzling pans beckons you to indulge. Feel the warmth of the curry as it spreads across your palate, savoring the delicate balance of flavors with each bite. Whether enjoyed as a simple weeknight dinner or served up at festive gatherings, Aloo Phulkopir Dalna is sure to leave a lasting impression on your taste buds and your heart.\n\nConclusion\n\nIn the world of Bengali cuisine, Aloo Phulkopir Dalna reigns supreme as a timeless classic  a dish that embodies the spirit of home and hearth. With its rich flavors, comforting textures, and soul-satisfying warmth, it is no wonder that this beloved curry holds a special place in the hearts of food enthusiasts around the world. So why not treat yourself to a taste of Bengali comfort food today? Whip up a batch of Aloo Phulkopir Dalna in your own kitchen and experience the magic for yourself.', 'blog_food_bengali.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/P4lvoKc__mc?si=1lI7dzBlsKnDeKLN\" title=\"YouTube video player', '', 'shizu', '2024-01-03', 2, 14, 'indianfood', '00:05:00'),
(79, 'Best Biryani in Melbourne ', 'Best Biryani in Melbourne at Ghazal Indian Restaurant', 'Savoring Melbourne\'s Finest: The Quest for the Best Biryani\n\nMelbourne, a melting pot of cultures and cuisines, is renowned for its vibrant food scene that caters to every palate. Among the myriad of culinary delights that grace the streets of this cosmopolitan city, one dish stands out as a true gem: Biryani. Embark on a culinary journey with us as we explore the tantalizing world of Biryani in Melbourne and discover where to find the very best this beloved dish has to offer.\n\nA Feast Fit for Royalty\n\nBiryani, a fragrant and flavorful rice dish that originated in the royal kitchens of ancient India, has captured the hearts and taste buds of food lovers around the globe. Comprising aromatic basmati rice, tender meat or vegetables, and a symphony of spices, Biryani is a feast fit for royalty. In Melbourne, where culinary diversity thrives, Biryani has found a home among the city\'s discerning diners, who seek out the finest renditions of this beloved dish.\n\nThe Hunt Begins\n\nWith so many restaurants and eateries vying for the title of Melbourne\'s best Biryani, the quest to find the ultimate culinary experience can seem daunting. Fear not, for we have scoured the streets and sampled the offerings to bring you a curated list of the top spots to indulge in this exquisite dish.\n\nServing Up Perfection: Melbourne\'s Top Biryani Destinations\n\nClaypots Evening Star: Nestled in the heart of South Melbourne, Claypots Evening Star is renowned for its delectable seafood dishes and vibrant atmosphere. Their Biryani, bursting with flavor and cooked to perfection, is a must-try for any discerning foodie.\n\nDosa Hut: With multiple locations across Melbourne, Dosa Hut is a favorite among locals for its authentic South Indian cuisine. Their Biryani, fragrant with spices and generously portioned, is sure to satisfy even the most discerning palate.\n\nLakshmi Vilas: Tucked away in the bustling suburb of Dandenong, Lakshmi Vilas is a hidden gem beloved by locals for its traditional Indian fare. Their Biryani, made with love and attention to detail, is a testament to the restaurant\'s commitment to excellence.\n\nZaaffran: Located on the banks of the Yarra River in Docklands, Zaaffran is renowned for its modern take on classic Indian dishes. Their Biryani, infused with the flavors of saffron and aromatic spices, is a culinary masterpiece that will leave you craving more.\n\nConclusion\n\nIn the vibrant culinary landscape of Melbourne, Biryani reigns supreme as a dish that transcends cultural boundaries and delights the senses. Whether you prefer it with tender pieces of meat, fragrant vegetables, or succulent seafood, there is no shortage of options to satisfy your craving for this beloved dish. So why not embark on your own Biryani adventure and discover the flavors that await you in Melbourne\'s diverse and dynamic food scene? With each bite, you\'ll experience a symphony of flavors that will transport you to the bustling streets of India and beyond.\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'blog_food_biryani.jpeg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/7SJh6vNR7jI?si=fQOJ2TTCIOdPDmMg\" title=\"YouTube video player', '', 'jenish', '2021-05-17', 2, 14, 'biryani', '00:05:00'),
(80, 'chocolate ragi pancakes', 'Pancakes are a beloved breakfast staple, loved for their fluffy texture and endless topping possibilities. But have you ever tried chocolate ragi pancakes? If not, you\'re in for a treat! These decadent delights combine the wholesome goodness of ragi flour with the rich, indulgent flavor of chocolate, creating a breakfast experience like no other. Join us as we delve into the world of chocolate ragi pancakes and discover why they\'re the perfect way to start your day.', 'Indulge Your Taste Buds: Chocolate Ragi Pancakes\n\nPancakes are a beloved breakfast staple, loved for their fluffy texture and endless topping possibilities. But have you ever tried chocolate ragi pancakes? If not, you\'re in for a treat! These decadent delights combine the wholesome goodness of ragi flour with the rich, indulgent flavor of chocolate, creating a breakfast experience like no other. Join us as we delve into the world of chocolate ragi pancakes and discover why they\'re the perfect way to start your day.\n\nThe Health Benefits of Ragi Flour\n\nRagi, also known as finger millet, is a nutrient-rich grain that has been a dietary staple in India for centuries. Packed with essential nutrients like calcium, iron, and fiber, ragi offers a myriad of health benefits. From supporting bone health to aiding digestion, incorporating ragi into your diet is a delicious way to nourish your body.\n\nThe Magic of Chocolate\n\nWho can resist the allure of chocolate? Rich, indulgent, and oh-so-satisfying, chocolate has been tantalizing taste buds for centuries. Not only does it satisfy your sweet tooth, but it\'s also packed with antioxidants that can benefit your heart health and improve your mood. When combined with ragi flour, chocolate transforms ordinary pancakes into a decadent treat that\'s as nutritious as it is delicious.\n\nHow to Make Chocolate Ragi Pancakes\n\nMaking chocolate ragi pancakes is easier than you might think. Simply combine ragi flour, cocoa powder, baking powder, and a touch of sweetness to create a fluffy, chocolatey batter. Cook the pancakes on a hot griddle until golden brown, then stack them high and top with your favorite toppings. Whether you prefer fresh berries, sliced bananas, or a drizzle of maple syrup, the possibilities are endless.\n\nWhy You\'ll Love Them\n\nChocolate ragi pancakes offer the perfect balance of indulgence and nutrition. They\'re a guilt-free way to satisfy your chocolate cravings while fueling your body with wholesome ingredients. Plus, they\'re incredibly versatile, making them suitable for breakfast, brunch, or even dessert. Whether you\'re a health-conscious foodie or simply looking to spice up your breakfast routine, chocolate ragi pancakes are sure to delight your taste buds and leave you craving more.\n\nConclusion\n\nIf you\'re tired of the same old breakfast routine, it\'s time to shake things up with chocolate ragi pancakes. With their rich, indulgent flavor and wholesome ingredients, they\'re the perfect way to start your day on a delicious note. So why wait? Whip up a batch today and treat yourself to a breakfast experience like no other. Your taste buds will thank you!', 'blog_food_chocolate.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/H2Cnmi-jnOo?si=W-9ti09rXm7U3dGd\" title=\"YouTube video player', '', 'prakash', '2023-11-21', 2, 14, 'chocolate', '00:05:00'),
